reviews: First day impression is audio works, outputs good sound, calls are clear at the other end so can say mic works too. Does its job and fulfil it purpose.But as far as overall feel good satisfaction is concerned, then have to say, item lives to its name. Its nothing but a piece of string, very very delicate; thin wires, thin 3.5 pin, thin bud caps. feels scary to hold and fold to carry in pocket, fear it might get pulled from some end breaking connector and stop working. Quality is not up to the mark and its not worth the money, should not pay more then rs70 to rs100.Disappointing that how unethical people have become just to do business. All they have done is, order cheap stuff from china, put their label and sell online with aim to make money. Wont be surprised if it does not live long enough, not durable at all. Wondering if its best to return for better quality product.Just to add - this is replacement item. First one received came with bad packaging and missing set of ear bud caps. it was looking dirty too as if used before... Amazon did a quick replacement, scores 10 out of 10 for quick response..Update:  there is a steel like ring on back top of the ear bud - which is not visible in the photo. Are you sure this is the correct item you have sent? or its a different version just cause it was in sale??
